{
  "stem": "25651.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was the word for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means compound.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there were-- in Auschwitz Birkenau, there were compounds of 10,000. 10,000 consisted of 30 barracks and two kitchen barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then there were four stalls barracks at the end of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The kitchens were at the gate of the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the camp was really fenced in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were the fences that went at right angles to the fences at the railway yards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We know nothing of the crematoria yet and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we're being tattooed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I'm with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there are some of the boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One of the Birkenau boys is five numbers away from me, Harry Goldenberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He's recently had a stroke, poor chap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We're all being tattooed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the man who-- the-- the-- the-- the Jewish prisoners who are tattooing, and my mother is ashen seeing that I'm going to be tattooed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She doesn't know where [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Milich ?] is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We don't see him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She's not yet tattooed, but I'm going to be tattooed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he says, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I won't hurt him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he does it very lightly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So with me, the-- the beginning numbers are sort of quite faint.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Can you see the one six is quite faint.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's 169067.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think Harry Goldberg is 169072.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you see the 1 and the 6 are faint?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the nine is a little bit heavier?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But even the rest of it isn't very heavy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it didn't hurt at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's doing this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sort of wipe it away and look at it as it's being done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the SS supervisor looks at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says to the-- says to the prisoner, strike it out and start again.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
